-- Billionaire Anil Ambani May Sell Stake in Reliance Infratel, Mint Reports
-- Anil Varma
-- 2010-06-14T01:43:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-14/anil-ambani-may-sell-stake-in-tower-unit-reliance-infratel-mint-reports.html

          
          
              Reliance Anil Dhirubhai Ambani
Group may sell a stake in its telecommunications towers unit
Reliance Infratel Ltd. before a proposed sale of shares in
Reliance Communications Ltd., the Mint newspaper reported,
without saying where it got the information.  
